	arts with two-days of traditional music\, step-dancing\, lectures\, geneal
	ogy workshops\, Irish films\, exhibits\, displays\, and more.\n\nhttps://w
	ww.seattlecenter.com/events/event-calendar/irish-festival-seattle-x46800
